quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  55,26,Buli kyonna ekigiriko (ensi) kya kuggwawo
  55,27,"Olwo nno wasigalewo obwennyini bwa Mukama omulabirizi wo, nannyini kugulumizibwa era nannyini kitiibwa"
  55,28,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,29,Bimusaba ebyo ebiri mu ggulu omusanvu n'ensi (naye nga) buli lunaku aba ku ngeri ndala (mu kugera kwe)
  55,30,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,31,"Tujja kubateerawo ekiseera abange mmwe ebitonde ebizito ebibiri (amajinni n’abantu, ekiseera ekyo mwe tulibalira buli omu)"
  55,32,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,33,"Abange mmwe ab'oluse lwa majinni n’oluse lwa bantu, bwe muba musobola okuyita mu bitundu bye ggulu omusanvu n'ensi (mube nga mudduka ku Katonda) kale muyitemu (naye) temuyinza kuyitamu okugyako nga mulina obusobozi"
  55,34,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,35,"Musindikirwa mwe ab'emirundi ebiri (amajinni n’abantu) ebitawuliro byomuliro, n’ekikomo ekisaanuuse (naye temusobola kwetaasa)"
  55,36,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,37,Olwo nno eggulu bwe liribajjuka nerirabika nga ekimuli ekimyufu (olwamaanyi g’omuliro) neriba nga omuzigo omusanuuse
  55,38,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,39,Ku lunaku olwo ekibi omuntu (kye yakola) tekigenda kubuuzibwa muntu mulala oba ejinni
  55,40,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,41,"Abonoonyi balimanyibwa olwobubonero bwabwe, olwo nno nebakwatibwa ku nviiri z’o mu buwompo n’ebigere (nebamenyebwamu nebakasukwa mu muliro)"
  55,42,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)
  55,43,Baligamba nti guno gwe muliro Jahannama abonoonyi gwe baali balimbisa
  55,44,Bagenda kwetoloolera wakati waagwo ne wakati w'olwegye oluyitirivu lwokwokya
  55,45,Kaakano kiriwa kye mulimbisa ku byengera bya Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe (mmwe ab’emirundi ebiri abantu na majinni)